{"tid":2073673,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（突發）獨立學社最新高質文宣","createTime":"2020-06-21T13:22:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-21T15:35:57.000Z","uid":18245,"like":55,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"7e8457476f22cb976c9c0339cb959b13b9eba2a9","tid":2073673,"uid":18245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T13:22:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=178646693686549&amp;id=103589494525603\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D178646693686549%26id%3D103589494525603&d=CgUtGs1XjGBKDnLe79D2YyPhHSzXeBMEaaQhzK3ZYsY%3D&h=9cd67345\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=178646693686549&amp;id=103589494525603</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WujGigY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWujGigY.jpg&h=d22cb92d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vQSAnJF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvQSAnJF.jpg&h=a44c9a3c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/APBYkvm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAPBYkvm.jpg&h=be79af52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n/​<br />\n🔥 奮 戰 到 底 🔥​<br />\n​<br />\n就算要拭去數千次眼淚也好，心中的革命之火仍然不會熄滅。​<br />\n​<br />\n星星之火，終會成為燎原的三昧真火，甚至幻化成一隻涅槃的浴火鳳凰。​<br />\n​<br />\n你願意一同飛往那絕世的天際嗎？​<br />\n​<br />\n來吧，讓我們繼續於蒼穹翱翔&mdash;&mdash;哪怕有閃電交加、狂風暴雨；即使天有多麼地高、即使羽翼消散紛飛也好。​<br />\n​<br />\n我們心中懷惴著的紅蓮之炎卻永不會熄滅，為這片土地驅逐漆黑中的絕望。​<br />\n​<br />\n而火之鳥亦不會停止振翅拍翼...... <br />\n<br />\n春蠶到死絲方盡，蠟炬成灰淚始乾。 <br />\n<br />\n📎海報高清印刷版下載:​<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1D3OILgsECX0IP4bcxIaU7ezh45HazlkG?usp=sharing​\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fdrive%2Ffolders%2F1D3OILgsECX0IP4bcxIaU7ezh45HazlkG%3Fusp%3Dsharing%E2%80%8B&d=CgUtGs1XjGBKDnLe79D2YyPhHSzXeBMEaaQhzK3ZYsY%3D&h=08ae50a6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1D3OILgsECX0IP4bcxIaU7ezh45HazlkG?usp=sharing​</a><br />\n​<br />\n或 tg: @hk_independence_insititue -​<br />\n​<br />\n#抗爭海報 #民族自強 #香港獨立 #光復香港 #時代革命 #主權在民 #奮戰到底"},{"pid":"0945a6ee9645bf85fc119dd2cf4be9b025a5a7c0","tid":2073673,"uid":88394,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T13:27:52.000Z","msg":"sorry, 見到d咁正嘅文宣一定要正評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 但係快手得滯篤錯咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3720a5784173087c6cddb75c213eff937c172893","tid":2073673,"uid":147376,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T13:31:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>☝️One Nation <br />\n☝️One Hong Kong<br />\n<br />\n☝️☝️</strong></span>"},{"pid":"63281cd3e700d51de842c69bfc1ec6297510c458","tid":2073673,"uid":147376,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T13:32:19.000Z","msg":"高清版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/drive/mobile/folders/1D3OILgsECX0IP4bcxIaU7ezh45HazlkG?usp=sharing%E2%80%8B\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fdrive%2Fmobile%2Ffolders%2F1D3OILgsECX0IP4bcxIaU7ezh45HazlkG%3Fusp%3Dsharing%25E2%2580%258B&d=CgUtGs1XjGBKDnLe79D2YyPhHSzXeBMEaaQhzK3ZYsY%3D&h=824e4321\" target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/drive/mobile/folders/1D3OILgsECX0IP4bcxIaU7ezh45HazlkG?usp=sharing%E2%80%8B</a>"},{"pid":"abba20c5b766b80a23fb442d81d3ee05db1d98e4","tid":2073673,"uid":22796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T13:34:21.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"a1bded606888699e0dc88827d7bb46f1a6adad99","tid":2073673,"uid":63311,"like":2,"dislike":9,"score":-7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T13:36:19.000Z","msg"