eplyTime":"2020-06-21T14:17:09.000Z","msg":"驟眼睇落有五成似<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n睇下佢哋歷史,絕對是手足,唔使派膠"},{"pid":"ab202ffaec23ad95e6b79ea541b6f78c760ef124","tid":2073673,"uid":318070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T14:18:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rZwp0LK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrZwp0LK.jpg&h=e738047f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y1AusqL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY1AusqL.jpg&h=a62b8f2e&s={SIZE}\" />6.28 靜默遊行 3時出發  <br />\n<br />\n本次行動本著以下原則進行<br />\n<br />\n不集合❗️不口號❗️不逗留❗️<br />\n<br />\n由佐敦A,B出口沿彌敦道行人道直到旺角解散<br />\n<br />\n⚠️請使用行人道進行本次行動<br />\n<br />\n❗️如被狗隻打斷或任何突發行動請轉入內街沿內街自行繼續/解散<br />\n<br />\n完成路程後請原地airdrop7.1有關文宣及離開<br />\n<br />\n本次行動為一個人抗爭系列之一"},{"pid":"f48e1ca58654dadfa01780216966dcb7ca6abd1a","tid":2073673,"uid":24345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T14:19:02.000Z","msg":"真係一路都咁高質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />文同圖都係"},{"pid":"8ce13776d9195312ede876b47dcf67845e92ffca","tid":2073673,"uid":136431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a1bded606888699e0dc88827d7bb46f1a6adad99","tid":2073673,"uid":63311,"like":2,"dislike":9,"score":-7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T13:36:19.000Z","msg":"獨立=痴人說夢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T14:20:40.000Z","msg":"中華民族偉大復興=南柯一夢"},{"pid":"aa9cc3586fc0edb8b01888c9ae7e431810080e76","tid":2073673,"uid":42548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T14:20:51.000Z","msg":"好似SHADOW OF RAIDER封面<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}